title: Ike's Place
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Sandwich shop with locations in the Bay area. Has a vegetarian section on the menu, all of which could be made vegan. Vegan choices include breaded vegan chicken, meatless meatballs, and turkey. Small, casual, counter-service, near San Ramon Valley High School.
